data.text:
WAYF Hi Low Dress

Hi everyone! In today's post I'm sharing this amazing WAYF hi low dress with you!

I saw this dress online and I immediately knew I had to have it. Part of the reason I love it so much is because of the price - you can't beat $88 for such a gorgeous dress. I love WAYF clothing because they're so affordable and made with GOOD quality. I have a few items by WAYF, and I know I need more from them.I wore this floral hi low dress to my cousins graduation in Maryland. Unfortunately, the weather did no cooperate with us and it was pretty rainy all weekend. We still had so much fun celebrating together. We finished off the trip with a whole lot of crabs - YUM! Getting back on topic - this dress was perfect for this type of occasion - not too fancy, but nice enough for a special event. Also, it can be dressed up with heels or great accessories. I paired it with my jean jacket from JCrew and I thought they looked great together! I love this dress so much that I am planning on investing in more WAYF items in the future!WAYF Hi Low Dress // JCrew Denim Jacket // Jack Rogers Sandals // David Yurman Bracelet // JCrew Bracelet // JCrew Factory Bracelet // Tory Burch Perry Tote My Mom's outfit: Loft Skirt // Loft Top // Tory Burch FlatsMy Aunt's outfit: Loft DressMy cousin's outfit: Anthropologie Dress // Jack Rogers SandalsI LOVED my cousin's graduation dress. I loved it so much that I think I want it for myself! She looked great in it and I love the style & the lace! It was seriously a perfect dress. I also loved the skirt and top that my mom wore! The skirt is perfect for summer and she paired it with such a pretty top! And my aunt's dress was SO cute and perfect for the occasion! It's safe to say I'm going to be doing some shopping very soon!

I hope you enjoyed this post about this WAYF hi low dress!

Thanks for reading!XO, Lauren
